        " اَلْبَاقِرُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «لِكُلِّ شَيْءٍ حُرْمَةٌ وَ حُرْمَةُ اَلْبَهَائِمِ فِي وُجُوهِهَا »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2472 - Abu Ja'far Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as)  said:\n\"Everything has a sanctity, and the sanctity of animals lies in their faces.\""
